data.title: News — KATIE MCCARTY
data.text:
wellness inc.

Katie is so excited to have been cast as a series regular for Wellness Inc. with Gladiolus Productions. She is thrilled to be portraying the lead role of Eliza!

SOHO International film festival NYC

Katie is so thrilled to have starred opposite Michael Kelberg in, “You Got Ma’amed,” and for the film to have been an Official Selection at the 2022 SOHO International Film Festival! NYC Premiere!

younger

Katie is thrilled to have been cast as Erin in season 6, Episode 5 of Younger.

Click "Learn More," below to visit the IMDB page for this episode.

The Blacklist

Katie is excited to have appeared in season 6 of The Blacklist, playing Molly in episode 4 entitled, “Pawnbrokers.”

Click "Learn More," below to visit the IMDB page for this episode.

Movie- MURDER AT THE MANSION

Katie is thrilled to have played Rosemary in, "Murder At The Mansion," starring Anna Hutchison, Jason-Shane Scott, Melissa Bolona, Audrey Landers and Kim Shaw, directed by Sam Irvin and produced by Stargazer Films.

Click "Learn More," below to visit the IMDB page for this movie.

Movie- A Very nutty christmas

Katie is so excited to have been cast as Tiffany in, "A Very Nutty Christmas," starring Melissa Joan Hart, directed by Colin Theys.

Click "Learn More," below to visit the IMDB page for this movie.

Movie- My daughter vanished-Lifetime

Katie is so thrilled to have been cast as Erin in a Stargazer Films' movie entitled, "My Daugter Vanished," airing in 2018 on Lifetime, directed by Sam Irvin.

Click "Learn More," below to visit the IMDB page for this movie.

Movie- You got ma'amed

Katie is so happy to have starred as Kate in the hilarious comedy, "You Got Ma'amed," a BluEye Productions' Film opposite actor Michael Kelberg.

Click "Learn More," below to visit the IMDB page for this movie.

Hallmark Christmas Movie

Katie is so thrilled to have been cast in a Christmas movie entitled, "Romance At Reindeer Lodge," airing December 17th on the Hallmark Channel.

Click "Learn More," below to visit the IMDB page for this movie.

national commercial- starring alongside Amara La Negra

Katie had the pleasure of starring alongside the beautiful and talented Amara La Negra, Dominican-American singer and star of the upcoming, "Love & Hip Hop: Miami," priemiering in January 2018. National Commercial coming this Spring, 2018.

Click "Learn More," below to check out an action shot of these two having fun on set!

A NATURAL DISASTER- FEATURE FILM

Katie is happy to have been cast as Jenny in the feature film, "A Natural Disaster," directed by Ananya Sundararajan and written by Claudio de Latour. This film is a romantic-horror-comedy about a dysfunctional marriage set it New York City during a hurricane. Shot on location in Crown Heights, Brooklyn, the film explores a relationship on edge amidst the hysteria of yet another calamity about to strike New York City.

Click "Learn More," below to visit the website for "A Natural Disaster," and to watch the trailer for the movie.

LAW AND ORDER SVU- KIRA

Katie is so excited to have been cast as Kira in Law and Order SVU: Season 18- Episode 5, "Rape Interrupted."

Click "Learn More," below to visit the IMDB page for this episode.

Rachel Dratch's Late Night Snack- TruTV

Katie is thrilled to be a part of, "Rachel Dratch's Late Night Snack," in "The Screen Test: Love Triangle In The Emergency Room."

Click "Learn More," below to check out the video.

My big gay Italian midlife crisis: off broadway comedy

Katie is beyond thrilled to join the cast of the hilarious Off Broadway comedy, "My Big Gay Italian MidLife Crisis." She joins original cast members as Lucia. The show plays at The Theater Center, NYC.

Click "Learn More," below to check out the BroadwayWorld Article for, "My Big Gay Italian MidLife Crisis."

The kloons- switching bodies

Katie is so excited to have been able to guest star on an episode of "Swiching Bodies," The Kloons: Season 2- Episode 8, "How To Pick Up Hot Chicks."
